1. *Mene* je sramota. (I am ashamed.)
2. Nema među *mene* nijednog dobrog čoveka. (There is not a single good man among me.)
3. Čovek je upravo kažnjavao *mene*. (The man was just punishing me.)
4. Ona se odnosila prema *mene* sa poštovanjem. (She treated me with respect.)
5. On misli da sam *mene* stvorio. (He thinks that I created myself.)
6. To je zato što *mene* ne razumeš. (That's because you don't understand me.)
7. Ona veruje u *mene*. (She believes in me.)
8. Ne mogu da verujem da *mene* ne poštuje. (I cannot believe that she doesn't respect me.)